{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":466,"text":"Four years ago today, exactly, actually,"},{"time":2563,"text":"I started a fashion blog called Style Rookie."},{"time":5659,"text":"Last September of 2011, I started an online magazine"},{"time":9779,"text":"for teenage girls called Rookiemag.com."},{"time":13654,"text":"My name's Tavi Gevinson, and"},{"time":17845,"text":"the title of my talk is \"Still Figuring It Out,\""},{"time":20985,"text":"and the MS Paint quality of my slides"},{"time":23232,"text":"was a total creative decision in keeping with today's theme,"},{"time":26544,"text":"and has nothing to do with my inability"},{"time":28160,"text":"to use PowerPoint. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":31505,"text":"So I edit this site for teenage girls. I'm a feminist."},{"time":36065,"text":"I am kind of a pop culture nerd, and I think a lot about"},{"time":38936,"text":"what makes a strong female character,"},{"time":41352,"text":"and, you know, movies and TV shows,"},{"time":43440,"text":"these things have influence. My own website."},{"time":47706,"text":"So I think the question of what makes a strong female"},{"time":50497,"text":"character often goes misinterpreted,"},{"time":52874,"text":"and instead we get these two-dimensional superwomen"},{"time":56167,"text":"who maybe have one quality that's played up a lot,"},{"time":59759,"text":"like a Catwoman type,"},{"time":62352,"text":"or she plays her sexuality up a lot,"},{"time":66230,"text":"and it's seen as power."},{"time":67422,"text":"But they're not strong characters who happen to be female."},{"time":70821,"text":"They're completely flat,"},{"time":72549,"text":"and they're basically cardboard characters."},{"time":75033,"text":"The problem with this is that then"},{"time":76866,"text":"people expect women to be that easy to understand,"},{"time":80712,"text":"and women are mad at themselves"},{"time":83039,"text":"for not being that simple,"},{"time":84381,"text":"when, in actuality, women are complicated,"},{"time":87338,"text":"women are multifaceted -- not because women are crazy,"},{"time":90736,"text":"but because people are crazy,"},{"time":92488,"text":"and women happen to be people. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":96150,"text":"So the flaws are the key."},{"time":98435,"text":"I'm not the first person to say this."},{"time":100278,"text":"What makes a strong female character"},{"time":102326,"text":"is a character who has weaknesses, who has flaws,"},{"time":107230,"text":"who is maybe not immediately likable,"},{"time":109214,"text":"but eventually relatable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111676,"text":"I don't like to acknowledge a problem"},{"time":113145,"text":"without also acknowledging those who work to fix it,"},{"time":115811,"text":"so just wanted to acknowledge shows like \"Mad Men,\""},{"time":118878,"text":"movies like \"Bridesmaids,\" whose female characters"},{"time":121758,"text":"or protagonists are complex, multifaceted."},{"time":125889,"text":"Lena Dunham, who's on here, her show on HBO"},{"time":130105,"text":"that premiers next month, \"Girls,\""},{"time":132296,"text":"she said she wanted to start it because she felt that"},{"time":134813,"text":"every woman she knew was just a bundle of contradictions,"},{"time":137801,"text":"and that feels accurate for all people,"},{"time":140009,"text":"but you don't see women represented like that as much."},{"time":142673,"text":"Congrats, guys. (Laughs)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":146257,"text":"But I don't feel that — I still feel that there are some types"},{"time":149960,"text":"of women who are not represented that way,"},{"time":152496,"text":"and one group that we'll focus on today are teens,"},{"time":154952,"text":"because I think teenagers are especially contradictory"},{"time":158232,"text":"and still figuring it out,"},{"time":161272,"text":"and in the '90s there was \"Freaks and Geeks\""},{"time":164621,"text":"and \"My So-Called Life,\" and their characters,"},{"time":167400,"text":"Lindsay Weir and Angela Chase,"},{"time":170056,"text":"I mean, the whole premise of the shows"},{"time":172744,"text":"were just them trying to figure themselves out, basically,"},{"time":176190,"text":"but those shows only lasted a season each,"},{"time":179288,"text":"and I haven't really seen anything like that on TV since."}]},{"cues":[{"time":184250,"text":"So this is a scientific diagram of my brain — (Laughter) —"},{"time":190636,"text":"around the time when I was,"},{"time":192108,"text":"when I started watching those TV shows."},{"time":194750,"text":"I was ending middle school, starting high school --"},{"time":196945,"text":"I'm a sophomore now —"},{"time":199209,"text":"and I was trying to reconcile"},{"time":201965,"text":"all of these differences that you're told you can't be"},{"time":204624,"text":"when you're growing up as a girl."},{"time":205971,"text":"You can't be smart and pretty."},{"time":208591,"text":"You can't be a feminist who's also interested in fashion."},{"time":211414,"text":"You can't care about clothes if it's not for the sake"},{"time":215308,"text":"of what other people, usually men, will think of you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":218341,"text":"So I was trying to figure all that out,"},{"time":221312,"text":"and I felt a little confused,"},{"time":224613,"text":"and I said so on my blog,"},{"time":226355,"text":"and I said that I wanted to start"},{"time":230540,"text":"a website for teenage girls"},{"time":233044,"text":"that was not this kind of one-dimensional"},{"time":236482,"text":"strong character empowerment thing"},{"time":239186,"text":"because I think one thing that can be very alienating"},{"time":242176,"text":"about a misconception of feminism is that"},{"time":244808,"text":"girls then think that to be a feminist, they have to live up to"},{"time":248403,"text":"being perfectly consistent in your beliefs,"},{"time":250894,"text":"never being insecure, never having doubts,"},{"time":254305,"text":"having all of the answers. And this is not true,"},{"time":257207,"text":"and, actually, reconciling all the contradictions I was feeling"},{"time":261260,"text":"became easier once I understood that feminism"},{"time":265019,"text":"was not a rulebook but a discussion,"},{"time":267206,"text":"a conversation, a process,"},{"time":269330,"text":"and this is a spread from a zine that I made last year"},{"time":272501,"text":"when I -- I mean, I think I've let myself go a bit"},{"time":275851,"text":"on the illustration front since."},{"time":277954,"text":"But, yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":281944,"text":"So I said on my blog that I wanted to start this publication"},{"time":286343,"text":"for teenage girls and ask people to submit"},{"time":288832,"text":"their writing, their photography, whatever,"},{"time":290952,"text":"to be a member of our staff."},{"time":292603,"text":"I got about 3,000 emails."},{"time":295527,"text":"My editorial director and I went through them and"},{"time":298199,"text":"put together a staff of people,"},{"time":301202,"text":"and we launched last September."},{"time":303802,"text":"And this is an excerpt from my first editor's letter,"},{"time":306157,"text":"where I say that Rookie, we don't have all the answers,"},{"time":309511,"text":"we're still figuring it out too, but the point is not to"},{"time":312240,"text":"give girls the answers, and not even give them permission"},{"time":316199,"text":"to find the answers themselves,"},{"time":318773,"text":"but hopefully inspire them to understand that"},{"time":320941,"text":"they can give themselves that permission,"},{"time":322664,"text":"they can ask their own questions, find their own answers,"},{"time":325548,"text":"all of that, and Rookie, I think we've been trying to make it"},{"time":328299,"text":"a nice place for all of that to be figured out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":333642,"text":"So I'm not saying, \"Be like us,\""},{"time":335577,"text":"and \"We're perfect role models,\" because we're not,"},{"time":337945,"text":"but we just want to help represent girls"},{"time":343057,"text":"in a way that shows those different dimensions."},{"time":346078,"text":"I mean, we have articles called"},{"time":349872,"text":"\"On Taking Yourself Seriously: How to Not Care What People Think of You,\""},{"time":353054,"text":"but we also have articles like,"},{"time":355021,"text":"oops -- I'm figuring it out!"},{"time":358982,"text":"Ha ha. (Laughter)"},{"time":361508,"text":"If you use that, you can get away with anything."},{"time":365306,"text":"We also have articles called"},{"time":366497,"text":"\"How to Look Like You Weren't Just Crying in Less than Five Minutes.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":370003,"text":"So all of that being said, I still really appreciate"},{"time":373036,"text":"those characters in movies and"},{"time":377003,"text":"articles like that on our site,"},{"time":378816,"text":"that aren't just about being totally powerful,"},{"time":382059,"text":"maybe finding your acceptance with yourself"},{"time":385109,"text":"and self-esteem and your flaws and how you accept those."}]},{"cues":[{"time":390668,"text":"So what I you to take away from my talk,"},{"time":394286,"text":"the lesson of all of this, is to just be Stevie Nicks."},{"time":398508,"text":"Like, that's all you have to do. (Laughter)"},{"time":401882,"text":"Because my favorite thing about her,"},{"time":404761,"text":"other than, like, everything, is that"},{"time":407821,"text":"she is very -- has always been"},{"time":410229,"text":"unapologetically present on stage,"},{"time":413134,"text":"and unapologetic about her flaws"},{"time":415941,"text":"and about reconciling all of her contradictory feelings"},{"time":420079,"text":"and she makes you listen to them and think about them,"},{"time":423671,"text":"and yeah, so please be Stevie Nicks."},{"time":425053,"text":"Thank you. (Applause)"}]}]}